OL,3,CTrump sacks US attorney general Pam
OL,4,CBondi
OL,6,FDonald Trump has sacked is attorney
OL,7,Fgeneral, Pam Bondi, after reports
OL,8,Fsuggested he had become increasingly
OL,9,Funhappy with her work, which included
OL,10,Fhandling the release of the Epstein
OL,11,Ffiles.
OL,13,FIn a post on his Truth Social social
OL,14,Fmedia account, the US president
OL,15,Fdescribed Bondi as a "great American
OL,16,Fpatriot" and said she had done a
OL,17,F"tremendous job."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
