OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1775250669
OL,3,CTrump sacks US attorney general Pam
OL,4,CBondi
OL,6,FHe added: "We love Pam, and she will
OL,7,Fbe transitioning to a much needed and
OL,8,Fimportant new job in the private
OL,9,Fsector."
OL,11,FIn the same social post, Trump named
OL,12,FDeputy Attorney General Todd Blanche
OL,13,Fas the acting attorney general.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
