OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1775250669
OL,3,CTrump sacks US attorney general Pam
OL,4,CBondi
OL,6,FIt marks the end of a contentious
OL,7,Ftenure of a loyalist who upended the
OL,8,FUS Justice Department's culture of
OL,9,Findependence from the White House,
OL,10,Foversaw large-scale firings of career
OL,11,Femployees, and moved aggressively to
OL,12,Finvestigate the Republican president's
OL,13,Fperceived enemies.
OL,15,FDespite this CNN reported Trump had
OL,16,Fbeen frustrated with Bondi on multiple
OL,17,Ffronts, including her handling of the
OL,18,FJeffrey Epstein files and that she had
OL,19,Fnot investigated or prosecuted enough
OL,20,Fof his political opponents.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
