OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1775250669
OL,3,CTrump sacks US attorney general Pam
OL,4,CBondi
OL,6,FThroughout the crisis around the
OL,7,Frelease of the Epstein files Trump
OL,8,Fconsistently defended Bondi, but he
OL,9,Falso grew frustrated with the issue as
OL,10,Fhis administration could not shake
OL,11,Fquestions about the president's
OL,12,Frelationship with the late disgraced
OL,13,Ffinancier.
OL,15,FBondi is the second cabinet member to
OL,16,Fbe ousted in recent weeks, with Trump
OL,17,Fremoving Kristi Noem as Secretary of
OL,18,Fthe Department of Homeland Security
OL,19,Flast month.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
